{"tid":489916,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"所謂世界頂尖企業，都可以犯咁低級的錯誤","createTime":"2017-12-05T07:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T03:35:44.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c09a276353a15221b99d6bba41db445068a52fc9","tid":489916,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:19:15.000Z","msg":"正版Win7在線更新功能報廢：用戶集體發飆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n按照微軟的規劃，對Windows 7系統的安全補丁更新會持續到2020年初。 不過，一些Win7用戶報告稱，Update功能出現了問題，提示80248015錯誤&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n按照微軟的規劃，對Windows 7系統的安全補丁更新會持續到2020年初。<br />\n<br />\n不過，一些Win7用戶報告稱，Update功能出現了問題，提示80248015錯誤，文字提示是&ldquo;Windows Update cannot currently check for updates because the service is not running. You may need to restart your computer（在線更新服務故障，請重啟電腦）&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n此外，ZDNet專家Mary Jo Foley遭遇的報錯是&ldquo;Windows could not search for new updates（Win無法搜索更新）&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n微軟論壇上的這一話題已經得到非常多的頂帖，Computerworld稱，這是微軟忘了給Win7延長授權期，文件定位到C:/Windows/SoftwareDistribution/AuthCabs/authcab.cab。解包后發現，內藏的XML文件中有個叫做authorization.xml，後者設定了一個到期時間是2017-12-03。<br />\n<br />\n目前有兩種臨時解決方法，一是停用更新檢查，二是將系統時間撥回到2017年12月2日之前。<br />\n<br />\n對於正版Win7用戶來說，這應當說是個比較嚴重的BUG，需要儘快修復。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.windowscentral.com/windows-7-updates-appear-be-broken-some\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.windowscentral.com%2Fwindows-7-updates-appear-be-broken-some&d=u6jx%2F9VOFGkjBxnBGyTxefjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=d08778da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.windowscentral.com/windows-7-updates-appear-be-broken-some</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.zdnet.com/article/windows-update-is-broken-for-some-windows-7-users/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zdnet.com%2Farticle%2Fwindows-update-is-broken-for-some-windows-7-users%2F&d=u6jx%2F9VOFGkjBxnBGyTxefjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=c7c07ae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.zdnet.com/article/windows-update-is-broken-for-some-windows-7-users/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.computerworld.com/article/3239729/microsoft-windows/windows-update-for-win7-broken-throwing-error-80248015.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.computerworld.com%2Farticle%2F3239729%2Fmicrosoft-windows%2Fwindows-update-for-win7-broken-throwing-error-80248015.html&d=u6jx%2F9VOFGkjBxnBGyTxefjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=7e83aad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.computerworld.com/article/3239729/microsoft-windows/windows-update-for-win7-broken-throwing-error-80248015.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.xcnnews.com/kj/2249441.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xcnnews.com%2Fkj%2F2249441.html&d=u6jx%2F9VOFGkjBxnBGyTxefjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=698bddc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.xcnnews.com/kj/2249441.html</a>"},{"pid":"12214f13a21092afc28ceb16789833c95390bb06","tid":489916,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/154156_07ed7a0a5a1b63976210d8f07ef8c039.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F05%2F154156_07ed7a0a5a1b63976210d8f07ef8c039.jpeg&h=bf56fd47&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c0d294b6fa0b1fa875b86e3aee7cc0392ce4070","tid":489916,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"呢個世界無嘢係完美"},{"pid":"9ac6df93e04a0a2518779473f4055b45f2f60048","tid":489916,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T23:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個世界無嘢係完美</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448944473a195841ae9bb2fe1f3b576df269fb71","tid":489916,"uid":28563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:29:00.000Z","msg":"正版用家受害者"},{"pid":"9ddfe8360a96a1f68df97bf8d9b575134dfaf28a